00:35:02,883 --> 00:35:04,145
Vex: No-stock，Nostoc？

926
00:35:04,145 --> 00:35:04,780
Vax: Nostoc。

927
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:06,705
Vex: Nostoc Grey⋯⋯spine。

928
00:35:06,705 --> 00:35:08,025
Adra: 對。

929
